item.title: Primary Edition
item.description: The Framework When the user opens the report platform, he will see title bar above, navigation bar on the left and content display area on the right. Under mobile devices, the navigation bar on the left side may be hidden automatically. Users need to click on of the title bar to expand the navigation bar to expand it. Report Management The navigation bar will use report category as the primary heading and report name as the secondary heading.
